</div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-1 span-1"><div class="sqs-block spacer-block sqs-block-spacer sized vsize-1" data-block-type="21" id="block-yui_3_17_2_1_1599165595144_11520"><div class="sqs-block-content">&nbsp;</div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-5 span-5"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-yui_3_17_2_1_1599165595144_9933"><div class="sqs-block-content">




<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <h3 style="white-space:pre-wrap; text-emphasis: initial;">Goals:</h3><ol data-rte-list="default">
    
    <li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Healthcare access and advocacy.</p></li>
    <p>The primary role of Texas Trans Coalition is to ensure all trans members of the community access authentic, timely and reliable health care. This promotes sustainable developement of the trans community in Texas.</p>
    <li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Legal recognition and justice.</p></li>
    <p>Texas Trans Coalition lobbies for inclusive for inclusive policies and legislation at the local, state and national levels that protect transgender rigths and ensure legal reconition of gender identity.</p>
    
</ol>
</div>



